{"article_id":"nLEwZJrujOumXuPT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Kentucky county clerk Kim Davis will appear in federal court today","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"to explain","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"why she believes","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"that God and her personal convictions empower her to break the law and deny gay people their constitutionally protected rights .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Ever since this summer ' s Supreme Court ruling in Obergefell v. Hodges ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"which legalized same-sex marriage nationwide ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Davis has been refusing to issue marriage licenses","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"- to any couple , gay or straight -","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"citing her religious beliefs .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"She was ordered by the governor to do her job ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"but she refused .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"She was ordered by a federal judge to do her job ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"but she refused .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"This week , the Supreme Court rejected her appeal of the federal judge ' s decision ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"which should have been the final word on the matter ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"but she ' s still refusing to the job","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"she was elected by the people of Kentucky to do .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"And so now she ' s being hauled before a judge","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"to determine","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"whether she ' s in contempt of court .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"There is no debate on that question :","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Davis is flagrantly in contempt","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and should be punished for what she ' s done .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"After the Supreme Court rejected her appeal ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"a gay couple confronted Davis","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and asked her to explain what authority she had","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to continue denying them their rights .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" God ' s authority , \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"she shot back ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"which is the absolute wrong answer for a government employee to provide .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"The Constitution is the governing power in Kim Davis ' office ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"and she is bound by oath to adhere to the law .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"She is breaking that oath ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"defying the Constitution ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"abusing her authority ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and insisting","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that she suffer no consequences for her behavior .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Davis ' illegal and morally dubious stand against gay marriage does appeal , however , to the slice of the conservative movement","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"that is hell bent on restoring the good old days of godly virtue","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"when you had the state ' s blessing","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"to discriminate against gay people .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"It just so happens that there are a number of Republican presidential candidates","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"who are trying to motivate that highly politically active segment of the population to get behind their campaigns ,","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"and that ' s led us to a situation","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"in which people","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"running for the nation ' s highest elected office","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"are cheering on a rogue government employee ' s defiance of the Constitution .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"If you were forced to guess which 2016 Republican candidate would line up behind Davis ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"you would of course choose Mike Huckabee ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"because Mike Huckabee is a crazy person","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"who says things like","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" the Supreme Court is not the supreme being ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and they can not overturn the laws of nature or of nature ' s god . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"And you would be 100 percent correct .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Here ' s Huckabee in South Carolina calling Kim Davis a hero","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"for defying the tyrants of the Supreme Court :","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"\" I salute her today ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and I stand with her , \"","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Huckabee said ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"explaining","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that he called her up","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to thank her","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"for standing up to \" judicial tyranny. \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Huckabee added :","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"\" I thank God for Kim Davis ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and I hope","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"more Americans will stand with her . \"","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Davis also got an attagirl from her home state senator and increasingly hopeless presidential contender , Rand Paul .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Rand wasn ' t quite so effusive in his praise of Davis as Huckabee ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"but he did say :","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"people","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"who do stand up","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"and are making a stand","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"to say","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"that they believe in something","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"is an important part of the American way. \"","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"He is correct","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that American history is full of people","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"who left their mark","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"by controversially standing up for their beliefs in defiance of the law","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"people like Orval Faubus , and George Wallace .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Rand explained","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"that his preferred policy would be to get states out of the marriage business altogether ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"which would potentially resolve the issue","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"but doesn ' t really speak to the immediacy of the problem at hand .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Davis also got a hearty endorsement from Bobby Jindal ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"who is somehow still running for president","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"despite polling in the mid to low zeroes .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"\" I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"anyone should have to choose between following their conscience and religious beliefs","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and giving up their job","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"and facing financial sanctions , \"","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Jindal said in a statement to the Huffington Post .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Not every Republican candidate is behind Davis","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"- Carly Fiorina , for example , has urged Davis to either give up or resign .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"But the situation could be complicated further","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"depending on how harshly Davis is punished by the courts .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"It ' s possible that Davis could land in jail for contempt ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"and","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"as ThinkProgress ' Ian Millhiser notes ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"as a prisoner she \" could inspire others to defy the Constitution","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"if she is perceived as a martyr. \"","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Were that to happen ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"we could see more would-be Republican presidents","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"championing brazen illegality in the service of anti-gay discrimination .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":213,"left":110,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":0,"right":109,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":1